    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const startTime = 8;\nconst finishTime = 17;\nconst operationDays = [1,2,3,4,5,6];\n`\n0 representa domingo,\n1 representa segunda-feira,\n2 representa terça-feira,\n3 representa quarta-feira,\n4 representa quinta-feira,\n5 representa sexta-feira,\n6 representa sábado.\n`\n\nconst now = new Date();\nconst nowHour = now.getHours();\nconst nowDay = now.getDay();\nif (nowHour >= startTime && nowHour < finishTime && operationDays.includes(nowDay)) {\n      return {size: 50000}\n    }\n\n return {size: 100000}"
